---
import PageLayout from "../layouts/PageLayout.astro";
import { site } from "../data/site";
---

<PageLayout
  title="Imprint - Allaia Media"
  description="Legal information about Allaia Media."
  eyebrow="Legal · Imprint"
  heading="Who's behind this."
  intro="Required legal information about who runs Allaia Media, where to find us, and how to reach us about anything official."
>
  <h2>Business</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Trading name:</strong> Allaia Media</li>
    <li><strong>Registered name:</strong> [Your registered company name]</li>
    <li><strong>Company number:</strong> [Your company registration number]</li>
    <li><strong>Registered address:</strong> [Your registered office address]</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href={`mailto:${site.email}`}>{site.email}</a></li>
    <li><strong>WhatsApp:</strong> <a href={site.whatsapp} target="_blank" rel="noopener">via wa.me</a></li>
    <li><strong>Instagram:</strong> <a href={site.instagram} target="_blank" rel="noopener">@allaia.media</a></li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Responsible for content</h2>
  <p>
    [Director / Founder name], reachable at the email above.
  </p>

  <h2>VAT / Tax</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>VAT number:</strong> [If applicable]</li>
    <li>Otherwise: not VAT-registered (under threshold).</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Markets we operate in</h2>
  <p>
    Allaia Media works remotely with founder-led brands across {site.markets.join(", ")}, and beyond on request. Invoicing is available in GBP, USD, AED, IDR, and PHP.
  </p>

  <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
  <p>
    Despite careful content review, we accept no liability for the content of external links. Operators of linked sites are solely responsible for their content. All trademarks and brand names referenced on this site belong to their respective owners.
  </p>

  <h2>Disputes</h2>
  <p>
    The European Commission provides an online dispute-resolution platform at <a href="https://ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr</a>. We're not obliged to and do not participate in dispute-resolution proceedings before a consumer arbitration board.
  </p>

  <h2>Copyright</h2>
  <p>
    All content on this site - copy, design, code, imagery - is &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Allaia Media unless otherwise noted. Client work shown in the portfolio remains the property of the respective clients.
  </p>
</PageLayout>
